male.name: eyewear
male.title: Angular Frames
male.desc: Angular frames add definition to round faces by creating contrast with the curves of the face.

male.name: hairstyle
male.title: Textured Crop
male.desc: Textured crops with short sides and a bit of height on top can elongate the face and add angles.

male.name: beardstyle
male.title: Square Beard
male.desc: A square beard can help create the illusion of a more angular jawline, balancing the roundness of the face.

male.name: cap
male.title: Flat Caps
male.desc: Flat caps can add some height to the crown of the head, creating a more elongated look for round faces.

female.name: eyewear
female.title: Cat-Eye Frames
female.desc: Cat-eye frames can add angles to a round face, creating a more balanced and elongated look.

female.name: hairstyle
female.title: Long Bob
female.desc: A long bob that falls just below the chin can create the illusion of a more oval face shape.

female.name: earrings
female.title: Dangle Earrings
female.desc: Dangle earrings can elongate the face, creating a more balanced look for round faces.

female.name: makeup
female.title: Contouring
female.desc: Contouring can help create shadows and definition along the sides of the face, especially on the temples, below the cheekbones, and along the jawline, to create a more sculpted look.
